\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2530002\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Aug 06, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104mnu1665702982711.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mnu1665702982711.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mnu1665702982711.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"mnu1665702982711\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Video Mode Mnemonics\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Video mode mnemonics define how the device displays characters in the various video modes and combinations.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mnu1665702982711__section_mzj_xzm_hcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d259954e51\">Arguments</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"mnu1665702982711__table_d5585e1_d5586e1_d5587e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Mnemonics for View Modes</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mnu1665702982711__table_d5585e1_d5586e1_d5587e1__entry__1\">Mnemonic </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"mnu1665702982711__table_d5585e1_d5586e1_d5587e1__entry__2\">Explanation </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mnu1665702982711__table_d5585e1_d5586e1_d5587e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">bli_hig</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mnu1665702982711__table_d5585e1_d5586e1_d5587e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Set video to blink and high intensity.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mnu1665702982711__table_d5585e1_d5586e1_d5587e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">bli_hig_inv</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mnu1665702982711__table_d5585e1_d5586e1_d5587e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Set video to blink, high intensity, and inverse.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mnu1665702982711__table_d5585e1_d5586e1_d5587e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">bli_hig_inv_und</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mnu1665702982711__table_d5585e1_d5586e1_d5587e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Set video to blink, high intensity, inverse, and underscore.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mnu1665702982711__table_d5585e1_d5586e1_d5587e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">bli_hig_und</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mnu1665702982711__table_d5585e1_d5586e1_d5587e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Set video to blink, high intensity, and underscore.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mnu1665702982711__table_d5585e1_d5586e1_d5587e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">bli_inv</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mnu1665702982711__table_d5585e1_d5586e1_d5587e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Set video to blink and inverse.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mnu1665702982711__table_d5585e1_d5586e1_d5587e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">bli_inv_und</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mnu1665702982711__table_d5585e1_d5586e1_d5587e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Set video to blink, inverse, and underscore.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mnu1665702982711__table_d5585e1_d5586e1_d5587e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">bli_und</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mnu1665702982711__table_d5585e1_d5586e1_d5587e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Set video to blink and underscore.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mnu1665702982711__table_d5585e1_d5586e1_d5587e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">blink</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mnu1665702982711__table_d5585e1_d5586e1_d5587e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Set video to blink.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mnu1665702982711__table_d5585e1_d5586e1_d5587e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">hig_inv</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mnu1665702982711__table_d5585e1_d5586e1_d5587e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Set video to high intensity and inverse.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mnu1665702982711__table_d5585e1_d5586e1_d5587e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">hig_inv_und</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mnu1665702982711__table_d5585e1_d5586e1_d5587e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Set video to high intensity, inverse, and underscore.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mnu1665702982711__table_d5585e1_d5586e1_d5587e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">hig_und</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mnu1665702982711__table_d5585e1_d5586e1_d5587e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Set video to high intensity and underscore.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mnu1665702982711__table_d5585e1_d5586e1_d5587e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">high</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mnu1665702982711__table_d5585e1_d5586e1_d5587e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Set video to high intensity.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mnu1665702982711__table_d5585e1_d5586e1_d5587e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">inv_und</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mnu1665702982711__table_d5585e1_d5586e1_d5587e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Set video to inverse and underscore.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mnu1665702982711__table_d5585e1_d5586e1_d5587e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">inverse</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mnu1665702982711__table_d5585e1_d5586e1_d5587e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Set video to inverse.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mnu1665702982711__table_d5585e1_d5586e1_d5587e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">novideo</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mnu1665702982711__table_d5585e1_d5586e1_d5587e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Reset to normal video.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mnu1665702982711__table_d5585e1_d5586e1_d5587e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">underscore</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"mnu1665702982711__table_d5585e1_d5586e1_d5587e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Set video to underscore.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"mnu1665702982711__pre_ewn_11n_hcc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">^027[0m ^NOVIDEO\n^027[28;22;25;4m ^UNDERSCORE\n^027[28;22;24;5m ^INVERSE\n^027[28;22;5;4m ^INV_UND\n^027[28;25;24;1m ^HIGH\n^027[28;25;1;4m ^HIG_UND\n^027[28;24;1;5m ^HIG_INV\n^027[28;1;5;4m ^HIG_INV_UND\n^027[22;25;24;8m ^BLINK\n^027[22;25;8;4m ^BLI_UND\n^027[22;24;8;5m ^BLI_INV\n^027[22;8;5;4m ^BLI_INV_UND\n^027[25;24;8;1m ^BLI_HIG\n^027[25;8;1;4m ^BLI_HIG_UND\n^027[24;8;1;5m ^BLI_HIG_INV\n^027[8;1;5;4m ^BLI_HIG_INV_UND\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lsj1665702873847.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Video Attributes</a><p>Video attributes determine the Uniface index colors used in an application, and additional attributes such as bold, blink, bright and underline used character mode that can be used to highlight current fields and occurrences.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530002\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530002\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Video Mode Mnemonics Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Aug 06, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Video Mode Mnemonics Video mode mnemonics define how the device displays characters in the various video modes and combinations. Arguments Table 1. Mnemonics for View Modes Mnemonic Explanation bli_hig Set video to blink and high intensity. bli_hig_inv Set video to blink, high intensity, and inverse. bli_hig_inv_und Set video to blink, high intensity, inverse, and underscore. bli_hig_und Set video to blink, high intensity, and underscore. bli_inv Set video to blink and inverse. bli_inv_und Set video to blink, inverse, and underscore. bli_und Set video to blink and underscore. blink Set video to blink. hig_inv Set video to high intensity and inverse. hig_inv_und Set video to high intensity, inverse, and underscore. hig_und Set video to high intensity and underscore. high Set video to high intensity. inv_und Set video to inverse and underscore. inverse Set video to inverse. novideo Reset to normal video. underscore Set video to underscore. ^027[0m ^NOVIDEO ^027[28;22;25;4m ^UNDERSCORE ^027[28;22;24;5m ^INVERSE ^027[28;22;5;4m ^INV_UND ^027[28;25;24;1m ^HIGH ^027[28;25;1;4m ^HIG_UND ^027[28;24;1;5m ^HIG_INV ^027[28;1;5;4m ^HIG_INV_UND ^027[22;25;24;8m ^BLINK ^027[22;25;8;4m ^BLI_UND ^027[22;24;8;5m ^BLI_INV ^027[22;8;5;4m ^BLI_INV_UND ^027[25;24;8;1m ^BLI_HIG ^027[25;8;1;4m ^BLI_HIG_UND ^027[24;8;1;5m ^BLI_HIG_INV ^027[8;1;5;4m ^BLI_HIG_INV_UND Copy Related Links Video Attributes Video attributes determine the Uniface index colors used in an application, and additional attributes such as bold, blink, bright and underline used character mode that can be used to highlight current fields and occurrences. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}